<HEADLINE>
FT  16 JAN 93 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
JOHANNESBURG weakened slightly in active trade with De Beers, 50 cents
higher at R68.75, again providing the main feature. The overall index lost 3
to 3,415, industrials fell 2 to 4,558 and the gold index slipped 4 to 788.
