<HEADLINE>
FT  16 JAN 93 / World Commodities Prices: Spices
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Mexican pimento prices have been firm, reports Man-producten. Spot increased
from USDollars 1,600 to Dollars 1,850 a tonne ex-warehouse Rotterdam;
